d. Inshallah very soon will have peace of mind…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Agar koi shakhs dil mein kisi qism ka khouf ya izteraab (be-chaini) rakhta ho to us ke liye yeh amal mujarrab (aazmaayi huwi) hai keh woh 9 din tak rozana 557 martaba is zikr ka vird kare. Inshallah bohot jald woh us khouf o izteraab se nikal aayega aur woh amn o itminaan haasil kar lega…", "UrduDescription": "اگر کوئی شخص دل میں کسی قسم کا خوف یا اضطراب رکھتا ہو تو اس کے لئے یہ عمل مجرب ہے کہ وہ 9 دن تک روزانہ 557 مرتبہ اس ذکر کا ورد کرے۔ انشاء اللہ بہت جلد وہ اس خوف و اضطراب سے نکل آئے گا اور وہ امن و اطمینان حاصل کرلے گا۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, 